lead_paragraph: Spain's Marc Marquez won the Argentine Grand Prix for Honda on Sunday to take the overall lead in the MotoGP standings after a shortened race overshadowed by concerns about tyre safety.

headline.print_headline: Marquez Wins in Argentina to Take Overall Lead
